Preheat the grill to a medium setting.Place 1 tablespoon of ricotta cheese and 1 tablespoon of lemon curd in the center of each of four crÃªpes.Fold up to make triangular packets open at the top.Place these in an ovenproof dish and spinkle on a little caster sugar. Dot with butter and cook under a medium grill, until the butter melts and the sugar crisps. Serve at once.